Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,On December 8th, 1941, \Nthe Rubicon was crossed. {lit: the war front target was drawn - think he means "the enemy has been designated and the point of no return crossed"}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.61,0:01:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We entered a state of war with our archenemies, \Nthe Anglo-Saxon nations. {/United States and Britain}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.06,0:02:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Early on this day, our elite troops landed in front of the enemy at Kota Bharu and Singora on the Malay Peninsula.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.09,0:02:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,At this time, the main force of the enemy's British Oriental Fleet, stationed in Singapore,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,urgently sailed north to attack our troops. {no clue what's hoshaku}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Upon receiving that intel, our fearless submarine fleet \Nwas dispatched to intercept and destroy it.
