Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the calm before the storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They watched their chances \Ndiminish by the minute. {lit: favourable time; opportunity was gradually passing by - think he means they disembarked but didn't advance until the sinking of prince of wales is confirmed}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.21,0:04:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No, their chances still hadn't peaked. {lit: No, favourable time was getting closer}
