Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.31,0:05:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy ship! They found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:32.16,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,500)}Enemy ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They've discovered the enemy Oriental Fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:34.26,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,500)}Enemy ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Our archenemy has taken the bait and is coming. {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:36.46,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,500)}Enemy ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. That's what we trained for. \NThat's what we trained for! {no idea, seems the language was a lot different in 1943}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:38.26,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,500)}Enemy ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.26,0:05:42.16,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,500)}Enemy ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.49,0:05:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Our front line soldiers have gained a foothold already. {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.23,0:05:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And come back alive!{\i0} {same}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.44,0:10:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible to see anything in this squall. \NIt's as though the sun had disappeared altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There were low rain clouds on the sea, \Nand we couldn't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.91,0:10:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, we had to return to the base.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.14,0:10:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The squall has cleared up, \Nbut there are no enemy ships in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.14,0:10:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We missed our big catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The heroes of the sky and the heroes of the sea \Ndrank from the cup of frustration that day. {lit: drank tears of regret}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,At dawn on December 10th, {no clue whats kakureba here, maybe "after laying low"}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the enemy ships were discovered once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, look! The gigantic ship advancing arrogantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.45,0:12:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The British Empire boasted it to the world as unsinkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.78,0:13:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,35,000 long tons, Prince of Wales.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.42,0:13:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Bow armament: one quadruple and one twin 14-inch gun turret.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Stern armament: one quadruple 14-inch gun turret.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A total of 10 main caliber guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.54,0:13:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There are also 16 anti-aircraft batteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.29,0:13:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And four seaplane catapults.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.14,0:13:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Among them, the most vaunted QF 2-pounder "pom-pom" gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Combined, the ship can fire \N60,000 rounds a minute. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.48,0:13:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,An unsinkable battleship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The Prince of Wales is a giant ship of the British Empire, \Nbrandished to the world with arrogance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.58,0:13:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is that other battleship?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.25,0:13:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell by its special mast.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:14:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Weighing 32,000 long tons, \Nthe second battleship is Repulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.59,0:14:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The main armament is a 15-inch gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,4 forward, 2 aft.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.51,0:14:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,6 in total.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.77,0:14:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,With 12 triple barreled anti-aircraft guns,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and four seaplane catapults.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Its cruising speed ​​is 31 knots. \NIt's the fast battleship Repulse. Repulse!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.78,0:14:31.18,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,500)}Found the enemy ships! {敵艦を発見す}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:34.15,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,500)}Found the enemy ships! {敵艦を発見す}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.15,0:14:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as we receive this news, \Nour strategy is immediately put into action.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:14:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Plane No. 3 of the long-range recon squadron finally reached the designated point,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.28,0:15:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but couldn't find the enemy fleet. {no clue what's sansei kikan banki}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They were running low on fuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.28,0:15:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We found their fleet!
