Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They knew they had to hold out until our attack aircraft arrived. {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:10.32,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,500)}Found the enemy ships! {敵艦を発見す}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:12.77,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,500)}Found the enemy ships! {敵艦を発見す}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Push on! \NDon't give up, Plane No. 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.77,0:17:15.97,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,500)}Found the enemy ships! {敵艦を発見す}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's our friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.52,0:17:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Our planes are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,More...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And more of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.38,0:17:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Loaded with bombs, \Nwith the torpedoes underneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.42,0:17:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the angels of victory we've been waiting for! {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll hammer the sea! {no clue, think the audio glitched here}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.35,0:17:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Can see the enemy fleet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.99,0:17:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the Prince of Wales!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.85,0:17:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The British vaunt it as the unsinkable battleship, \Nbut that's only because no one's sunk it yet. {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.73,0:17:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, let's sink it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.69,0:17:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's sink it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:18:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now’s the time to show them \Nthe Japanese spirit of achieving the impossible! {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.08,0:18:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's up to us to sink Repulse!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.71,0:18:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sink Repulse!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sink Repulse!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a hit! We've hit Repulse!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.22,0:18:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Repulse caught fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The mast has fallen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.10,0:18:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's burning! Burning! It's on fire! \NRepulse is on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.61,0:18:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's burning here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We've scored a hit on "Wales!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Miserable and wretched, \Ntrying to run away—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.34,0:19:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,such is the fate of the pride of Britain's Oriental Fleet, with which she intended to "rule the waves" on the seven seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.31,0:19:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"Wales" is burning, \Nfinish off Repulse!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:20:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince of Wales is sinking. \NRepulse is sinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.81,0:20:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the end of Prince of Wales, \Nand the end of Repulse!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It submerged underwater!\N{\i1}It's going down!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's still too early to rejoice. \NThe first ship is still afloat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, the first ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have the "Wales" to sink!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let "Wales" escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.80,0:20:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't let "Wales" escape!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.68,0:20:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got nowhere to escape now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot! Shoot! Shoot at the "Wales!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.99,0:20:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot at the "Wales!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.55,0:22:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over, both our engines caught fire. \NThey caught fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.12,0:22:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't fired our torpedo yet. \NStill haven't fired. Still haven't fired!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.78,0:22:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There, it's fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.83,0:22:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the machine marches forward. \NIt marches steadily forward!{no clue, could be not about torpedo but about their plane}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.26,0:22:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right on course. \NRight on course. Right on course! {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.60,0:22:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The smoking ships, the setting sun, \Nthe torpedoes, fired by our heroic comrades...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.07,0:22:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.61,0:22:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one scored! {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.70,0:22:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The water column rose high!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.31,0:22:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We got "Wales!"\NWe got "Wales!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.47,0:23:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,"Wales" is listing! \N"Wales" is listing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.24,0:23:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The man deck is underwater! {no clue, hear "listing until/to osmething"}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.99,0:23:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She' taking water! \NWe got her! We got her!
